claim by Levrard et. al., who found that all orbital and\nspin parameters evolve on a similar timescale to orbital decay.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2010 18:37:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Oct 2010 22:33:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Oct 2010 15:28:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
